Identified 1.Air pollution is high in haldia and khana place compared to other places
2.The year 2014 and 2008 has more air pollution
3.Manipur state has more air pollution
4.MAPB and VRCE helps to reduce the air pollution
5.Industrial area pollute more
6.The pm25 is more in 30-36 frequency rate
7.no2 is high in frequency level 11
8.spm is highest rate is 600
9.pm25 is at its peek on 36 frequency level
10.so2 level is more the air pollution increases
